      <meta>
         <dc:title xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">row-spacing-and-footer</dc:title>
         <dc:description xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Tests row spacing combined with footer. The last row of a page before the footer has no rowgap. If a gap is desired an empty footer line must be inserted.</dc:description>
